{
  "texts": [
    "Meanwhile, existing studies also reduce the computation cost by using the distributed model training [681] and dynamic GPU memory manager [682].• BRM data enrichment.",
    "The challenge of training datasets can be alleviated as the exponential growth in the number of bug reports.",
    "BRM studies also adopt DL techniques such as fine-tuning [647] and transfer learning [668] to address this problem.",
    "In addition, we can automatically generate (relatively low-quality) artificial data to enlarge the training set.",
    "Typically, data generation is treated in a case-bycase manner."
  ]
}